repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The materials consist of photographs of Yale athletic events, associations and facilities. Included are shots of practices, teams, individual athletes, cheerleaders, and games. Also included are posters, lithographs and engravings from nineteenth-century magazines. Baseball, crew, football, swimming, and track are particularly well documented.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-C (YRG 38-C), Audiovisual materials and memorabilia documenting athletics at Yale.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.
Access to Accession 2008-A-065 is by appointment only. Contact the Head of Public Services or the Public Services Manager.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale Athletics Photographs (RU 691). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The pictures are arranged by sport, thereunder chronologically and in subsequent accessions.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of photographs of Yale athletic events, associations and facilities. Included are shots of practices, teams, individual athletes, cheerleaders, and games. Also included are posters, lithographs and engravings from nineteenth-century magazines. Baseball, crew, football, swimming, and track are particularly well documented.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Accession 2017-A-060 gift of Anne Hall Connor, 2017.
